long.am,ar,bg,bn,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_U:
TruthGPT(developed by Singularity Labs) aims to be a "maximum truth-seeking" AI. TruthGPT's goal is to eliminate hallucination. It is designed to prioritize accurate information, and be a counterweight to existing chatbots like ChatGPT™ and Gemini™, which have been criticized for spreading false information or harmful rhetoric. TruthGPT is a AI chatbot with the potential to address some of the challenges of AI safety and disinformation. 

TruthGPT for Google™ extension is a version of TruthGPT (developed by Singularity Labs) which integrates TruthGPT with Google™ search results. It automatically triggers query to ChatGPT™ when you search for anything on google and then validates the generated information using Google's Bard chatbot.

No ChatGPT™ Plus plan required.

Colour Code meaning:
* RED - false
* YELLOW - it may be true or false(the verifier is not sure)
* GREEN - true

Make sure you Pin it to use later .

For feedback or feature requests reach out to us at https://github.com/SingularityLabs-ai/truthgpt-for-google-extension-mini/issues


LEGAL:
Disclaimer: TruthGPT for Google™ is not official Google™ Application. It is an unofficial extension that is developed and maintained independently and has no affiliation to Google™ .
long.ca,de,es,es_419,fr,he,hu,ko,pt_BR,pt_PT,:
TruthGPT aims to be a "maximum truth-seeking" AI. It is designed to prioritize accurate information over anything else, and to be a counterweight to existing chatbots like ChatGPT and Bard, which have been criticized for spreading false information or harmful rhetoric.
But TruthGPT uses both ChatGPT and Bard to validate truthfulness of a given information.

TruthGPT is a AI chatbot model with the potential to address some of the challenges of AI safety and disinformation. 

Colour Code meaning:
* RED - false
* YELLOW - it may be true or false(the verifier is not sure)
* GREEN - true

Make sure you Pin it to use later .

TruthGPT has the potential to be a powerful tool for promoting truth and accuracy in the world. TruthGPT aims to minimize disinformation and hallucinations.

For feedback or feature requests reach out to us at https://github.com/SingularityLabs-ai/truthgpt-for-google-extension-mini/issues
